## Suggested Commands

```bash
# Create branch
git checkout -b fix/cloudflare-runtime-risk-scoring

# After writing script
chmod +x infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh
bash -n infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh
infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh --help
infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh --markdown
infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh --json | python3 -m json.tool

# Secret check
grep -RInE '(token|secret|password|credential|api[_-]?key)' \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-risk-scoring.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-risk-scorecard-template.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-risk-gate-policy.md \
  infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh || echo "No secrets found"

# Commit
git add docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-risk-scoring.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-risk-scorecard-template.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-risk-gate-policy.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-report.md \
        infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh \
        infra/cloudflare/scripts/validate-cloudflare-config.sh \
        infra/cloudflare/README.md
git commit -m "docs(cloudflare): add runtime risk scoring gates"

git push origin fix/cloudflare-runtime-risk-scoring
gh pr create --title "docs(cloudflare): add runtime risk scoring gates" \
  --body "Phase 17: Adds offline risk scoring system for Cloudflare changes (DNS/Worker/Tunnel/IaC). Includes scoring script, scorecard template, gate policy. Read-only. No deploy. No secrets."
```

